subject: Auctions
Horses
Horse Racing
Breeders' Cup (Horse Race)
lead_paragraph: Awesome Feather, the winner of the Breeders’ Cup Juvenile Fillies race Friday, was sold at auction two days later for $2.3 million at the Fasig-Tipton November Sale in Lexington, Ky.
